			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Triggered if SwD is cast on the body (once free of the tunnel, cast is blocked otherwise)\r\n\r\nTo trigger GREETING\r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. goto 416.76; 37.801; -46.394\r\n4. addDebugSpell Target_SpeakWithDead\r\n5. infiniteAp\r\n6. Use the speak with dead spell to start dialog."
				},
